{"tid":1579121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外國人唔知香港人點解仲要繼續，不如整條片用英文旁述","createTime":"2019-09-18T12:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T08:21:02.000Z","uid":184973,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5d64a479d5f59bc418037857136bfbcee4bab83e","tid":1579121,"uid":184973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:18:30.000Z","msg":"去到外國，好多外國人都問發生咩事，都徹回左點解仲要放曬火咁。<br />\n<br />\n相信外國媒體都一樣，比火光呢啲eye catchy野吸引到/嘩眾取寵。加上好多資料都係用中文所以外國人睇唔明，以致佢地嘅資訊唔全面。<br />\n<br />\n所以我拋磚引玉，建議不如整條片放上YouTube(見有關嘅英文片都一兩個月前好唔update)，以香港人嘅身分綜合下呢三個月嘅重大事件，有幾多人犧牲，警方政府有幾過份。最緊要係有英文字幕同旁述。<br />\n<br />\n我自問冇能力整條高質片放上YouTube。因此希望呢到各位大神巴絲打一齊幫手，同關注香港事態發展嘅外國朋友解釋番我地面對緊嘅軍政府有幾無法無天。<br />\n<br />\nps 好少連登開po，有咩唔啱規矩/奇怪請多多指教。"},{"pid":"a467b21fb4ae2d0c6812e51e5131bfdfbeb9d536","tid":1579121,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:18:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2de4a6d44a4bb0ddfef6408a27e32577e3faf105","tid":1579121,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:19:10.000Z","msg":"[援助] 前線義士唔單止要開飯，要gear，仲要&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579059</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"00db2647bb51912354b6ab9b3d51db1d41a53405","tid":1579121,"uid":136700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,